public abstract class OutServe
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable

DolphinNet
Benjamin E. Coe (2006)

This class provides an abstract basis for sending outbound data on a socket. You must implement the getGuiObject() which checks for objects to be output and the specialInit() method which is provided for any implementation specific initialization.
